Double Punch/Manterror/Injector/Bumblebee:


The four Predacons had now left the Predacon base, in search of Hell Beast.  
Trying to follo wthe sound of Double Punch's voice.

"Hell Beast better be this way, Punch, or I'm goin to beat the living slag 
out of ya!" Manterror yelled.

"Same here, you bucket of bolts." Injector joked.

Bumblebee was thinking of making a similar comment, but he wasn't sure if 
Double Punch would be offended and kill him, or laugh.  So he decided to just 
shut up.
